race.comment: CRAFT (5) is third up and ready to show his best form. Will find this more suitable than Randwick last time and winning rider Heywood is reunited. He's left the one to beat. CARAVANSERAI (4) registered a comfortable win at Cootamundra before a narrow defeat over 1600m at Goulburn. He is free-running and at the peak of his form. Definitely a key player in this line-up. KEN'KER (7) turned in a better effort finding a place at the Sapphire Coast 5 days ago. This is tougher, but he maps well and carries 3kg less. He has claims as well. CYBORG (2) peaks and has won this course/trip. It's been a long time between drinks for him.
